---
import PageContainer from "../components/PageContainer.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy — hmziq.rs" description="Privacy policy for hmziq.rs.">
  <PageContainer>
    <PageHeader
      title="Privacy"
      description="A concise explanation of what this site collects, what it does not collect, how analytics are used, and how advertising appears on the site."
      class="mb-8"
    />
    <article class="prose legal-doc max-w-3xl">
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-base-300 bg-base-200 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-base-content/62">
          Policy
        </span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-base-content/48">
          Effective March 31, 2026
        </span>
      </div>

      <p>
        hmziq.rs is a read-only publication. It does not offer account creation, user logins, paid
        memberships, comment systems, or email newsletters. In normal use, you can browse the site
        without directly submitting personal profile information.
      </p>

      <h2>What this site collects</h2>
      <p>
        The site uses Firebase Analytics to understand overall traffic and general usage patterns.
        Depending on Google&apos;s analytics processing, that may include information such as browser
        type, device category, approximate location, referring source, page views, and interaction
        events.
      </p>

      <h2>What this site does not collect</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not designed around user accounts or marketing funnels. It does not maintain
        subscriber databases, authentication records, or profile dashboards for readers.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        hmziq.rs may display static advertising or sponsorship placements alongside content. Those
        placements are part of the page presentation and are not currently described here as
        behaviorally targeted advertising based on reader profiles.
      </p>

      <h2>How analytics data is used</h2>
      <p>
        Analytics information is used to understand how the site is read and to improve content,
        performance, and navigation. It is not used to build advertising profiles or to sell access
        to reader data.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party processing</h2>
      <p>
        Firebase Analytics is operated by Google, and its processing is subject to Google&apos;s own
        terms and privacy documentation. Normal hosting, caching, and delivery infrastructure may
        also process technical request data as part of serving the site. If the site later adopts a
        third-party advertising network or ad-serving platform, this page may be updated to reflect
        that change.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have a privacy-related question about hmziq.rs, use the details listed on the
        <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. Material changes to this page may be reflected here by
        updating the effective date.
      </p>
    </article>
  </PageContainer>
</BaseLayout>
